OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782751678
OL,3,CWoman dies after going missing in a
OL,4,Cpool near West Bromwich
OL,6,FA woman has died after being recovered
OL,7,Ffrom a pool in Sandwell Valley Country
OL,8,FPark.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,Fpark after the 55-year-old woman went
OL,12,Fmissing in the water just after 4.30
OL,13,Fpm yesterday.
OL,15,FSpecialist teams from fire and rescue
OL,16,Fwere deployed into the water, where
OL,17,Fthey recovered the body.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
