CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782751678
OL,3,CWoman dies after going missing in a
OL,4,Cpool near West Bromwich
OL,6,FDespite efforts by the rescue team,
OL,7,Fshe was confirmed dead at the scene in
OL,8,Fthe country park between Birmingham
OL,9,Fand West Bromwich.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police have said they
OL,12,Fare supporting the woman's family at
OL,13,Fthis tragic time.
OL,15,FA statement from the force said: "Our
OL,16,Fthoughts are with her family at this
OL,17,Ftragic time.
OL,19,F"Her death is not being treated as
OL,20,Fsuspicious at this time and we will be
OL,21,Fliaising with the coroner."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
