OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782751678
OL,3,CWoman dies after going missing in a
OL,4,Cpool near West Bromwich
OL,6,FIt comes after two other people died
OL,7,Fin the Midlands connected with open
OL,8,Fwater.
OL,10,FA 22-year-old man's body has been
OL,11,Frecovered from a river after it was
OL,12,Freported he got into difficulty during
OL,13,Fthe heatwave, police said.
OL,15,FBrody Leach's body was recovered from
OL,16,Fthe River Severn in Shrewsbury,
OL,17,FShropshire, on Saturday morning, West
OL,18,FMercia Police said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
