PN,34404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782751678
OL,3,CWoman dies after going missing in a
OL,4,Cpool near West Bromwich
OL,6,FA teenage boy also died after he
OL,7,Fentered a lake to 'cool off' during
OL,8,Fthe heatwave in Leicestershire.
OL,10,FHayden Jones-Powell, 13, went missing
OL,11,Fafter going for a swim at Meynell Lake
OL,12,Fon Thursday, June 25.
OL,14,FIn a tribute, his family has described
OL,15,Fthe West Bromwich Albion fan as a
OL,16,F'cheeky boy.'
